      "level": {
        "value": 12
      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role (B16):</strong> the four erinyes bound to Ileosa by the A90 contract — <strong>Decabbara, Eveanie, Suishani, Verasia</strong> — her bodyguard-furies. On the PCs' <em>first</em> castle assault, one waits with the A17 guard-devils and <strong>teleports to the Sunken Queen to report</strong> rather than fight. At rest they meditate at B16; they teleport to the queen's side the instant she is attacked (B20), and investigate B2 if looting is sensed there — retreating to her at half HP in that errand only. Contract-bound: otherwise they fight to the death, in shrieking pairs, ropes first.</p>",
      "publication": {
